column7: Wouldn’t you know, if yours truly has a Valentine’s gig, it’ll be followed by one on Pi Day. Except on leap years. But the point here is that I thought about doing a show themed on circles, spheres, and other such expressions of the number and decided against it, but keep your ears pealed for some future incarnation of a “Round and Round” playlist. Instead, tonight we kick things off with the sort-of eponymous track from **The Nude Party**’s latest release, and wrap things up with about 30 seconds of Railroad Jerk, because technical difficulties.
